You are receiving this email from Affirm Financial Services (AffirmFinancial.ca), Station B, Box 53, London, Ontario N6A 4V3. Note that this e mail was sent to {!Application__c.Email_Address__c}. If you received this e mail at a different address, this e mail message was forwarded. If you do not wish to receive e mails from us about products, services or offers, please <a href="https://www.affirmfinancial.ca/unsubscribe/">click here</a> to unsubscribe.
